OL,3,CShock at scale of Police Ombudsman
OL,4,Cinvestigation into ex officer accused
OL,5,Cof rape
OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's Police Ombudsman
OL,8,Fhas revealed the extent and size of
OL,9,Fits investigation into one former
OL,10,Fpolice officer accused of multiple
OL,11,Fsexual offences including rape while
OL,12,Fon duty.
OL,14,FIn an unprecedented move, the
OL,15,Finvestigation is so big the ombudsman
OL,16,Fis diverting all available resources
OL,17,Fto the one case.
OL,19,FJustice Minister Naomi Long expressed
OL,20,Fher shock at the size of the
OL,21,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773227361
OL,3,CShock at scale of Police Ombudsman
OL,4,Cinvestigation into ex officer accused
OL,5,Cof rape
OL,7,FDetails of the case, first revealed by
OL,8,FUTV, allege a former officer committed
OL,9,Fmore than 10 sexual offences and
OL,10,Fmisconduct in public office between
OL,11,F2000 and 2009.
OL,13,FHe left the PSNI under a cloud after a
OL,14,Fmisconduct hearing.
OL,16,FIt has now been confirmed that
OL,17,Fmultiple potential victims have been
OL,18,Fidentified as well as a substantial
OL,19,Fnumber of witnesses.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773227361
OL,3,CShock at scale of Police Ombudsman
OL,4,Cinvestigation into ex officer accused
OL,5,Cof rape
OL,7,FIn a statement, Chief Executive of the
OL,8,FPolice Ombudsman, Hugh Hume said: "We
OL,9,Fhave also seized a large volume of
OL,10,Fmaterial, including a significant
OL,11,Famount of digital evidence, during a
OL,12,Fsearch operation.
OL,14,F"We understand that this news may be
OL,15,Fdistressing for anyone who has been
OL,16,Faffected or harmed or who has been
OL,17,Fharmed by a similar experience.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773227361
OL,3,CShock at scale of Police Ombudsman
OL,4,Cinvestigation into ex officer accused
OL,5,Cof rape
OL,7,F"We would like to reassure victims
OL,8,Fthat they are not to blame and if they
OL,9,Fchoose to contact us, we will listen,
OL,10,Fwe will investigate and we will do so
OL,11,Findependently from police."
OL,13,F"As the victim impact, scale and
OL,14,Fcomplexity of the investigation have
OL,15,Fbecome clear, we are now working to
OL,16,Fensure that this investigation is
OL,17,Fcarried out in the most timely manner
OL,18,Fpossible. We are, therefore,
OL,19,Fallocating all available resources to
OL,20,Fensure it will be victim-centred,
OL,21,Feffective and efficient.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773227361
OL,3,CShock at scale of Police Ombudsman
OL,4,Cinvestigation into ex officer accused
OL,5,Cof rape
OL,7,F"Our resources are finite and this
OL,8,Fmeans that the timeliness of our other
OL,9,Fcasework may be affected. However,
OL,10,Fthis is the reality of balancing the
OL,11,Fdemands of our complaints across the
OL,12,FOffice with the need to progress this
OL,13,Fcomplex and expanding investigation.
OL,14,FIf we do not prioritise now, in the
OL,15,Flong term we risk compromising the
OL,16,Fservice we provide to complainants and
OL,17,Fvictims, and public confidence in this
OL,18,Foffice and the PSNI."
OL,20,FThe Justice Minister says its right
OL,21,Fthe case is prioritised.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773227361
OL,3,CShock at scale of Police Ombudsman
OL,4,Cinvestigation into ex officer accused
OL,5,Cof rape
OL,7,FNaomi Long MLA "It's so important that
OL,8,Fthese predatory individuals are able
OL,9,Fto be brought before the courts and
OL,10,Fheld accountable for their actions.
OL,11,FIt's particularly important where
OL,12,Fthey're predatory individuals within
OL,13,Fthe police service, because many
OL,14,Fvulnerable people will come in contact
OL,15,Fwith the police every day."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773227361
OL,3,CShock at scale of Police Ombudsman
OL,4,Cinvestigation into ex officer accused
OL,5,Cof rape
OL,7,FThe minister continued: "We have to
OL,8,Fprovide that reassurance that this is
OL,9,Fnot the police service of today, that
OL,10,Fthis would not be repeated today, and
OL,11,Fthat the proper safeguards are in
OL,12,Fplace so that people are not in any
OL,13,Fway dissuaded or fearful about coming
OL,14,Fforward. That's important for me as
OL,15,FJustice Minister, and particularly in
OL,16,Fthe work we're doing around violence
OL,17,Fagainst women and girls."
OL,19,FPolice welcome the ombudsman's
OL,20,Finvestigation and say they are fully
OL,21,Fco-operating with it.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
