OL,3,CShock at scale of Police Ombudsman
OL,4,Cinvestigation into ex officer accused
OL,5,Cof rape
OL,7,FLast week the PSNI Chief Constable
OL,8,Fdidn't hold back on what he had to say
OL,9,Fabout who those betray their badge for
OL,10,Fmore sinister purposes.
OL,12,FIn Jon Boutcher's opening remarks to
OL,13,Fthe policing board he said "any abuse
OL,14,Fof position for sexual purposes is not
OL,15,Fsimply wholly unacceptable, it's
OL,16,Fabhorrent".
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,19,FITVX
